OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and widely sunny day
OL,6,Ftoday across the region. Some cloud
OL,7,Fbubbling up later in the day with an
OL,8,Foutside chance of a thunderstorm.
OL,9,FAnother hot day with temperatures way
OL,10,Fabove average for the time of year.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine and warm evening for
OL,13,Fmany, although still the risk of the
OL,14,Fodd thunderstorm at first. Remaining
OL,15,Fwarm overnight with plenty of clear
OL,16,Fskies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
