OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day,
OL,6,Falthough some cloud may move into the
OL,7,Ffar west of Cornwall and the Isles of
OL,8,FScilly. Not as hot but still feeling
OL,9,Fvery warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FStaying largely dry and settled,
OL,13,Falthough a few showers may develop
OL,14,Ffrom time to time. Very warm initially
OL,15,Fbut it will begin to cool a little by
OL,16,Fthe weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
